* 6 servo support
* easy configurable
	* each servo configurable:
		*	Trim center
		*	Max position
		*	Min position
		*	Fail position
		*	Expo rate
		*	Rate speed
		*	Reverse
	* Fail save timeout
	* 9 different control designs
	* RC model name
	* Access Point(AP) mode or connect to existing WiFi
	* SSID
	* Password
* includes possibility to hard reset to "factory" settings
* in case of wrong SSID or Password in non AP mode after 5 min triggers reset to "factory" settings
* "factory" settings SSID includes MAC
